name: Venom Panda - KuD-056
description: He used to be a common civilian in pandas universe, work in daylight and rest at night. But one night a meteor falls in his neighborhood, and that meteor bring unknown lifeform with it. Like a slime with black color, it looks not dangerous so he approach it. But something unexpected happened, that slime envelop his entire body and taking control of his limbs. He became something new, something that he cannot control, full of bloodlust and feeling hungry because of this parasite need some nutrients to maintain its existence. Therefore he as a creature engulfed by parasite starting to hunt for food by killing anything alive, and there began a massacre.
